== Overview ==
The Plasma Turbo-Cannon is the heaviest version of [[Plasma Cannon]] available to Controllers. High capacity dual plasma chambers and a cyclic magnetic launcher allow this weapon to fire plasma at a very rapid rate. It is however extremely heavy.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Plasma Turbo-Cannon can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Plasma Technology]].
